*Gledaju* se u ogledalo. (They are looking at themselves in the mirror.)

Oni *gledaju* dokumentarce. (They are watching a documentary.)

Ona *gleda* unazad. (She is looking back.)

*Gledala* je u daljinu. (She was looking in the distance.)

*Gledamo* kako se pomera oblak. (We are watching a cloud move.)

Oni *gledaju* sa strane. (They are looking from the side.)